  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check">Verify context &lt; 60%. If higher, run `context-handoff` before proceeding.</step>
    <step order="0.5" name="Invoke fluent-v9-component">Invoke `Skill fluent-v9-component` (binding per design.md §6.0). Load `fluent-v9-portal-gotcha.md`, `fluent-v9-component-authoring.md`, `fluent-v9-theming.md` before reading any Fluent v9 file.</step>
    <step order="1" name="Load knowledge">Read ADR-006, ADR-012, ADR-021, ADR-022, ADR-028; load PCF CLAUDE.md and PCF-DEPLOYMENT-GUIDE.md. Read existing `ResultCard.tsx`, `FilePreviewDialog.tsx`, `SemanticSearchControl.tsx`, `AiSummaryPopover.tsx` to map existing handlers (Preview, AI Summary, Open File, Find Similar, Open Record, Email, Copy Link, Workspace, Download, Pin, Rename, Delete) to the 13 menu actions.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Import shared DocumentRowMenu">In `ResultCard.tsx`, import `DocumentRowMenu`, `IDocumentRowMenuTarget`, `DocumentRowAction` from `@spaarke/ui-components`. Confirm the shared library version pulled by the PCF includes task 012's barrel export.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Replace inline icons in ResultCard">In `ResultCard.tsx`, replace the row's inline action icons with a `MoreVertical20Regular` trigger button rendering `DocumentRowMenu`. Pass `document` as the `IDocumentRowMenuTarget`. Map `onAction` callback to a dispatch table that invokes the existing handlers (preview/openFile/findSimilar/openRecord/email/copyLink/workspace/download/pin/rename/delete) and AI Summary popover open. Trigger button MUST have `appearance="subtle"`, `size="small"`, and `onClick` handler that calls `e.stopPropagation()` BEFORE the menu opens.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Preserve AiSummaryPopover">Confirm the sparkle icon + `AiSummaryPopover` hover affordance remains in `ResultCard.tsx`. The menu's "AI summary" item invokes the SAME popover trigger (keyboard access). Both coexist — do NOT remove the sparkle.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Replace dialog-toolbar icons">In `FilePreviewDialog.tsx`, replace the dialog-toolbar action icons (Open Record / Email / Copy Link / Workspace) with the same `DocumentRowMenu` mounted in the dialog header. The same dispatch table is reused. Preserve dialog close/find-similar/open-file footer actions (those move under FR-DOC-03 task 044, not here).</step>
    <step order="6" name="Wire permission scoping">If existing code computes per-document permissions (e.g., `canDelete`, `canRename`), pass them to `DocumentRowMenu` via `disabledActions` prop — do NOT hide menu items, disable them per FR-SC-02 contract.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Verify no orphaned affordances">Grep `ResultCard.tsx` and `FilePreviewDialog.tsx` for any remaining inline icon buttons (Open File, Find Similar, Preview, Open Record, Email, Copy Link, Workspace, Download, Pin, Rename, Delete) — only the sparkle for `AiSummaryPopover` and the new `MoreVertical20Regular` trigger should remain.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Dark-mode + a11y check">Run PCF in dev harness with `webLightTheme` and `webDarkTheme`; verify menu, trigger button, and `AiSummaryPopover` render with v9 tokens; verify keyboard navigation (Tab to trigger → Enter to open → Arrow to navigate → Enter to invoke action) works.</step>
    <step order="9" name="Build verification">Run `npm run build:prod` from `src/client/pcf/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl/`. Verify clean build. PCF bundle size delta &lt; 5 KB.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality gates (FULL rigor)">Invoke `Skill code-review` then `Skill adr-check`. Resolve every finding before completion. `code-review` enforces `/fluent-v9-component` invocation — if Step 0.5 was skipped, merge is blocked.</step>
    <step order="10" name="Checkpoint">Run `context-handoff` (silent: ✅ Checkpoint).</step>
    <step order="11" name="Update task tracking">Update `projects/spaarke-matter-ui-enhancement-r1/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: task 040 status 🔲 → ✅. Reset `projects/spaarke-matter-ui-enhancement-r1/current-task.md` to next pending task (likely 041).</step>
  </steps>

